			<td valign="top">
				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The APU frame sequencer does not run at the same rate as the PPU's frame.  The number of PPU cycles that makes up a frame is irrelevant, as it has no effect on how the APU runs. 
<br />
<br />1 APU "frame" != 1 PPU frame
<br />
<br />I actually find the word frame a little misleading.</div>

